1928;;Say It with Sables;;American;;Frank Capra;;Francis X. Bushman, Helene Chadwick;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Say_It_with_Sables;;Doug Caswell (Arthur Rankin) falls for Irene Gordon (Margaret Livingston). Irene happens to be the mistress of his wealthy father, John Caswell (Francis X. Bushman), and it's up to Doug's stepmother, Helen (Helene Chadwick) to put things right.